{"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pullrequests/128/comments/68415283.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pull-requests/128/_/diff#comment-68415283"}}, "parent": {"id": 68414244, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pullrequests/128/comments/68414244.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pull-requests/128/_/diff#comment-68414244"}}}, "deleted": false, "pullrequest": {"type": "pullrequest", "id": 128, "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pullrequests/128.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/ignitionrobotics/ign-gui/pull-requests/128"}}, "title": "[gz11] Application"}, "content": {"raw": "Sorry :confused:\n\nMaybe this could be a clearer API?\n\n~~~\nignition::gui::Application app(_argc, _argv, kMainWindow);\napp.LoadConfig(config);\napp.LoadPlugin(plugin);\napp.exec();\n~~~\n\n* Prevents loading config/plugin before window initialization\n* Enforces window initialization\n* Downstream developers still have the flexibility to configure the app before exec", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Sorry <img class=\"emoji\" src=\"data/pf-emoji-service--cdn.us-east-1.prod.public.atl-paas.net/standard/551c9814-1d37-4573-819d-afab3afeaf32/48x48/1f615.png\" alt=\"\ud83d\ude15\" title=\":confused:\" data-emoji-short-name=\":confused:\" /></p>\n<p>Maybe this could be a clearer API?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">ignition</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">gui</span><span class=\"p\">::</span><span class=\"nd\">Application</span> <span class=\"nt\">app</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">_argc</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">_argv</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"nt\">kMainWindow</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">app</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nc\">LoadConfig</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">config</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">app</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nc\">LoadPlugin</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"nt\">plugin</span><span class=\"o\">);</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">app</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"nc\">exec</span><span class=\"o\">();</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Prevents loading config/plugin before window initialization</li>\n<li>Enforces window initialization</li>\n<li>Downstream developers still have the flexibility to configure the app before exec</li>\n</ul>", "type": "rendered"}, "created_on": "2018-06-27T22:51:22.613164+00:00", "user": {"display_name": "Louise Poubel", "uuid": "{5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B5cfa2075-477b-4ded-bdb9-8d2479544ec4%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8/7d903d90-c5ea-4182-b7ef-0d467e9e1c74/128"}}, "nickname": "chapulina", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:6ff86fcb-b7ab-44a5-b8a6-f6d9cae8b6e8"}, "updated_on": "2018-06-27T22:51:22.620321+00:00", "type": "pullrequest_comment", "id": 68415283}